1
00:00:01,560 --> 00:00:02,359
Zhai Qiuyu

2
00:00:04,519 --> 00:00:05,320
You're too kind.

3
00:00:13,039 --> 00:00:16,039
How many people do you think will stay by your side?

4
00:00:19,399 --> 00:00:20,239
What did you say?

5
00:00:21,079 --> 00:00:21,920
I said,

6
00:00:23,000 --> 00:00:24,079
Eventually,

7
00:00:25,440 --> 00:00:27,519
you'll be left all alone.

8
00:00:35,359 --> 00:00:36,000
Qiuyu,

9
00:02:30,039 --> 00:02:30,719
You're awake.

10
00:02:31,759 --> 00:02:33,080
Feeling any better?

11
00:02:34,240 --> 00:02:35,520
What are you doing here?

12
00:02:39,039 --> 00:02:40,319
Gu Hao asked me to come.

13
00:02:40,439 --> 00:02:41,560
There was a last-minute issue at the club.

14
00:02:41,879 --> 00:02:42,800
He had to leave early.

15
00:02:43,439 --> 00:02:44,479
He asked me to look after you.

16
00:02:46,199 --> 00:02:47,000
Thank you.

17
00:02:54,159 --> 00:02:55,039
Zhai Qiuyu

18
00:02:57,599 --> 00:02:58,599
How is he?

19
00:02:59,280 --> 00:03:00,319
They haven't figured it out yet.

20
00:03:00,759 --> 00:03:02,039
I'm already investigating.

21
00:03:02,639 --> 00:03:03,879
What I mean is,

22
00:03:04,560 --> 00:03:05,800
is he okay?

23
00:03:07,400 --> 00:03:08,879
He can't take much of a scolding.

24
00:03:09,400 --> 00:03:10,919
He hit Chen Mo after the competition.

25
00:03:11,719 --> 00:03:13,759
Now we're waiting for the committee's decision on the penalty.

26
00:03:14,560 --> 00:03:15,639
Is he injured?

27
00:03:17,039 --> 00:03:18,479
You're so upset about it,

28
00:03:19,319 --> 00:03:20,439
and you're still worried about him?

29
00:03:26,639 --> 00:03:27,879
It's my fault.

30
00:03:29,719 --> 00:03:31,919
I wish I hadn't met Chen Mo.

31
00:05:09,240 --> 00:05:10,600
At this hour?

32
00:05:11,120 --> 00:05:12,720
You still have time to ask me out?

33
00:05:15,160 --> 00:05:15,959
People...

34
00:05:21,519 --> 00:05:22,360
Chen Mo.

35
00:05:36,079 --> 00:05:37,040
Finally here.

36
00:05:37,720 --> 00:05:39,000
Let's take things one by one.

37
00:05:39,240 --> 00:05:40,279
You can't sell me out.

38
00:05:41,360 --> 00:05:42,439
Why aren't you saying anything?

39
00:05:43,279 --> 00:05:44,560
You're quite cautious, aren't you?

40
00:05:45,040 --> 00:05:46,439
I have to go back and tell Brother Qiu Yu.

41
00:05:49,759 --> 00:05:50,519
Zhou Song

42
00:05:50,519 --> 00:05:51,839
Guess what I saw?

43
00:05:55,240 --> 00:05:56,040
No

44
00:05:56,120 --> 00:05:57,040
It wasn't Teacher Li

45
00:05:57,160 --> 00:05:58,240
What nonsense are you talking about?

46
00:06:01,639 --> 00:06:02,600
You're finally here.

47
00:06:03,279 --> 00:06:04,560
Let's take things one by one.

48
00:06:04,800 --> 00:06:05,839
You can't sell me out.

49
00:06:06,920 --> 00:06:08,000
Why aren't you saying anything?

50
00:06:08,839 --> 00:06:10,120
You're quite cautious, aren't you?

51
00:06:12,399 --> 00:06:13,560
Even if it wasn't him

52
00:06:14,120 --> 00:06:15,000
he should still be secretly

53
00:06:15,000 --> 00:06:16,759
contacting people from other clubs?

54
00:06:30,000 --> 00:06:30,800
Brother Qiuyu

55
00:06:31,000 --> 00:06:31,959
Stop drinking

56
00:06:33,680 --> 00:06:34,279
Just stop

57
00:06:34,279 --> 00:06:35,160
Brother Qiuyu

58
00:06:41,399 --> 00:06:42,240
Get a grip

59
00:06:44,759 --> 00:06:45,560
Brother Qiuyu

60
00:06:47,759 --> 00:06:49,120
Hurry up and call Li Youen

61
00:07:18,680 --> 00:07:20,079
Why haven't you left yet?

62
00:07:26,480 --> 00:07:27,279
No way.

63
00:07:27,360 --> 00:07:28,560
I still have to go back and check.

64
00:07:31,480 --> 00:07:33,600
Help this time, and there'll be a next time.

65
00:07:34,000 --> 00:07:35,680
Might as well let them sort it out themselves.

66
00:07:35,920 --> 00:07:36,879
Be thorough.

67
00:07:58,600 --> 00:07:59,959
I told you to leave, why didn't you?

68
00:08:01,240 --> 00:08:03,000
Why aren't you listening to me either?

69
00:08:03,680 --> 00:08:04,279
No.

70
00:08:04,279 --> 00:08:06,000
Zhai Qiuyu, let me explain.

71
00:08:07,000 --> 00:08:08,240
No, it's not like that.

72
00:08:09,639 --> 00:08:11,240
You're here to laugh at me?

73
00:08:11,879 --> 00:08:13,120
You want to tell Chen Mo

74
00:08:13,120 --> 00:08:14,680
about my current state, right?

75
00:08:15,519 --> 00:08:16,360
I didn't.

76
00:08:16,920 --> 00:08:17,759
I didn't.

77
00:08:17,839 --> 00:08:18,680
I didn't.

78
00:08:19,759 --> 00:08:20,560
Don't.

79
00:08:22,680 --> 00:08:24,040
How dare you scheme against me?

80
00:08:24,360 --> 00:08:25,759
Who do you think you are?

81
00:08:26,519 --> 00:08:28,360
How dare you use my injury to scheme against me?

82
00:08:31,120 --> 00:08:31,920
Zhai Qiuyu

83
00:08:32,519 --> 00:08:33,440
Your elbow

84
00:08:34,159 --> 00:08:35,120
is fine

85
00:08:35,919 --> 00:08:37,480
Let me put some medicine on it for you

86
00:08:38,759 --> 00:08:39,559
What are you doing?

87
00:08:40,639 --> 00:08:41,679
Pity me

88
00:08:46,559 --> 00:08:47,360
I'll need a

89
00:08:47,360 --> 00:08:49,240
Someone who sells themselves to pity me?

90
00:08:53,000 --> 00:08:53,720
You

91
00:08:55,440 --> 00:08:56,480
What did you say?

92
00:09:00,519 --> 00:09:02,080
Don't let me see you again.

93
00:09:17,440 --> 00:09:18,679
You don't believe I didn't do it.

94
00:09:20,559 --> 00:09:22,399
You also don't believe I genuinely care about you.

95
00:09:27,480 --> 00:09:29,320
Why don't you just believe me?

96
00:09:39,720 --> 00:09:40,960
No matter how much you hurt,

97
00:09:41,120 --> 00:09:43,200
you have to stand firm on the field.

98
00:09:44,440 --> 00:09:45,320
I didn't.

99
00:09:45,440 --> 00:09:46,519
It really wasn't me.

100
00:09:46,919 --> 00:09:47,720
Zhai Qiuyu,

101
00:09:48,440 --> 00:09:51,360
count how many people you can keep by your side.

102
00:10:56,919 --> 00:10:57,720
Brother

103
00:10:59,519 --> 00:11:00,440
The doctor asked me to ask you

104
00:11:00,440 --> 00:11:01,679
if you want to go through the discharge process

105
00:11:02,600 --> 00:11:03,279
Discharge

106
00:11:03,279 --> 00:11:03,919
Yeah

107
00:11:03,919 --> 00:11:05,120
He said my condition is stable

108
00:11:05,120 --> 00:11:06,399
and I just need regular check-ups

109
00:11:09,080 --> 00:11:09,759
Brother

110
00:11:09,919 --> 00:11:12,759
Why do you look so troubled?

111
00:11:20,120 --> 00:11:20,960
It's good to be discharged too

112
00:11:29,720 --> 00:11:30,440
Xiaosi

113
00:11:31,320 --> 00:11:32,840
Why don't we go back to our hometown?

114
00:11:33,639 --> 00:11:35,080
A few days ago, my cousin asked me

115
00:11:35,159 --> 00:11:36,559
if I wanted to go back and do batik dyeing.

116
00:11:37,039 --> 00:11:38,600
He has a vacant shop.

117
00:11:38,919 --> 00:11:39,720
Okay!

118
00:11:40,240 --> 00:11:41,480
Wherever brother goes, I go.

119
00:11:58,120 --> 00:11:58,720
Gu Hao

120
00:12:00,159 --> 00:12:01,120
Have you seen Qiu Yu?

121
00:12:01,399 --> 00:12:02,120
Is he here today?

122
00:12:02,159 --> 00:12:03,799
Brother Qiu Yu probably won't be here today.

123
00:12:04,080 --> 00:12:05,240
He got really drunk last night.

124
00:12:05,320 --> 00:12:06,039
Got drunk.

125
00:12:07,120 --> 00:12:08,519
How can you still be in the mood to drink at a time like this?

126
00:12:09,080 --> 00:12:09,559
I'll go find him.

127
00:12:10,000 --> 00:12:10,559
Guidance

128
00:12:11,759 --> 00:12:13,000
Zhai Qiuyu has Teacher Li to look after him.

129
00:12:13,200 --> 00:12:14,039
You don't need to worry.

130
00:12:14,240 --> 00:12:14,960
Teacher Li is still here.

131
00:12:15,120 --> 00:12:16,159
Teacher Li is already leaving.

132
00:12:18,879 --> 00:12:19,679
Leaving?

133
00:12:20,600 --> 00:12:21,639
Where are you going?

134
00:12:34,559 --> 00:12:35,360
Brother,

135
00:12:35,440 --> 00:12:37,000
Is it that old man again?

136
00:12:37,399 --> 00:12:39,120
Why does your club have so many problems?

137
00:12:40,559 --> 00:12:41,480
He's a friend.

138
00:12:45,919 --> 00:12:46,720
Hello?

139
00:12:47,720 --> 00:12:48,480
Teacher Li,

140
00:12:49,120 --> 00:12:50,080
why are you resigning?

141
00:12:51,759 --> 00:12:53,159
This whole thing blew up so big.

142
00:12:53,879 --> 00:12:54,799
If I stay any longer,

143
00:12:55,279 --> 00:12:56,360
I'm afraid I'll be an eyesore to him.

144
00:12:56,879 --> 00:12:58,279
But that matter has already been cleared up.

145
00:12:58,919 --> 00:12:59,919
It was Chen Mo's people who did it.

146
00:13:00,919 --> 00:13:02,120
Didn't Brother Qiu Yu tell you?

147
00:13:03,399 --> 00:13:04,120
He knows.

148
00:13:05,879 --> 00:13:06,600
Teacher Li

149
00:13:07,120 --> 00:13:08,039
You come back first.

150
00:13:08,200 --> 00:13:09,759
We can talk about it when we meet.

151
00:13:10,679 --> 00:13:11,080
Hello?

152
00:13:11,919 --> 00:13:12,399
Hello?

153
00:13:13,960 --> 00:13:15,320
So he knows everything.

154
00:13:26,759 --> 00:13:27,320
Brother

155
00:13:38,639 --> 00:13:40,000
Isn't that Brother Qiu Yu?

156
00:13:40,840 --> 00:13:42,159
It feels like I haven't seen him in ages.

157
00:13:42,159 --> 00:13:43,320
What happened to him?

158
00:13:44,159 --> 00:13:44,799
I don't know.

159
00:14:05,279 --> 00:14:06,679
Can't this be discussed over the phone?

160
00:14:07,440 --> 00:14:08,360
Why did you have to call me over here?

161
00:14:10,360 --> 00:14:11,879
How much longer do you plan on staying home?

162
00:14:12,799 --> 00:14:13,919
Look at you now.

163
00:14:14,440 --> 00:14:16,320
You don't look like a tennis player at all.

164
00:14:18,679 --> 00:14:19,639
You called me over

165
00:14:20,399 --> 00:14:21,600
just to mock me?

166
00:14:26,879 --> 00:14:28,200
To look at the new Team Doctor Kang's files.

167
00:14:28,440 --> 00:14:30,200
Your elbow rehabilitation needs supervision.

168
00:14:30,559 --> 00:14:31,200
Fine.

169
00:14:33,159 --> 00:14:35,000
It's a good thing I wanted to fire Li Youen anyway.

170
00:14:35,320 --> 00:14:37,679
He hasn't shown up for days.

171
00:14:38,320 --> 00:14:39,480
I don't even know where he went.

172
00:14:39,639 --> 00:14:40,559
You fire him?

173
00:14:41,240 --> 00:14:42,720
He already fired you.

174
00:14:51,080 --> 00:14:51,600
He

175
00:14:53,240 --> 00:14:54,360
He resigned.

176
00:14:54,519 --> 00:14:55,480
Regretting it now?

177
00:14:55,879 --> 00:14:57,279
It's too late to regret it.

178
00:15:28,600 --> 00:15:29,360
Fine.

179
00:15:29,879 --> 00:15:30,960
Good riddance.

180
00:15:31,360 --> 00:15:32,840
Worst case, I'll just find another one.

181
00:16:06,600 --> 00:16:07,039
I

182
00:16:07,480 --> 00:16:08,559
I didn't mean to.

183
00:16:21,799 --> 00:16:22,679
Brother Qiuyu

184
00:17:17,599 --> 00:17:19,279
Why don't you believe me?

185
00:17:19,960 --> 00:17:20,759
Why?

186
00:17:42,000 --> 00:17:42,920
Brother Qiu Yu

187
00:17:43,720 --> 00:17:45,160
Have you found a team doctor you like?

188
00:17:45,480 --> 00:17:46,920
Director Wang gave so much money

189
00:17:49,920 --> 00:17:50,839
Forget I said anything.

190
00:17:57,480 --> 00:17:58,279
Zhai Qiuyu

191
00:17:58,799 --> 00:18:00,000
You're recovering quite quickly.

192
00:18:01,440 --> 00:18:02,559
Don't talk nonsense.

193
00:18:03,240 --> 00:18:04,480
Be careful not to agitate him.

194
00:18:05,359 --> 00:18:06,680
They've been back for several days.

195
00:18:06,680 --> 00:18:07,920
They haven't said a word.

196
00:18:08,039 --> 00:18:09,160
They've gone mute.

197
00:18:10,759 --> 00:18:11,759
Don't talk nonsense.

198
00:18:15,759 --> 00:18:17,319
The team doctor must be gone.

199
00:18:17,880 --> 00:18:19,759
He's not feeling well in any aspect, is he?

200
00:18:19,759 --> 00:18:20,720
You're overthinking it.

201
00:18:21,839 --> 00:18:23,240
It's not like I can't do without him.

202
00:18:28,640 --> 00:18:29,440
Brother Qiuyu,

203
00:18:32,480 --> 00:18:34,039
he should just be left alone.

204
00:18:34,519 --> 00:18:35,640
Think it through.

205
00:18:54,079 --> 00:18:55,240
Where have you been these past few days?

206
00:19:06,440 --> 00:19:07,240
Who are you?

207
00:19:07,559 --> 00:19:08,680
What are you doing at my doorstep?

208
00:19:12,079 --> 00:19:14,119
Mr. Zhou Song sent me here.

209
00:19:21,559 --> 00:19:23,480
I'll give you something you can't do without.

210
00:19:29,640 --> 00:19:31,559
Mr. Zhai, relax.

211
00:19:31,799 --> 00:19:33,240
I'll keep you company tonight.

212
00:19:34,079 --> 00:19:34,759
Get lost.

213
00:19:36,599 --> 00:19:37,799
So Mr. Zhai

214
00:19:37,920 --> 00:19:39,680
likes to play hard to get.

215
00:19:40,079 --> 00:19:41,160
I'm good at that too.

216
00:19:49,519 --> 00:19:50,359
I told you to get lost.

217
00:19:50,359 --> 00:19:51,839
Can't you understand plain English?

218
00:19:52,759 --> 00:19:54,640
Disappear from my sight immediately.

219
00:19:56,480 --> 00:19:57,480
You should have just said no.

220
00:19:57,640 --> 00:19:58,799
What a waste of a handsome face.

221
00:19:59,079 --> 00:20:00,519
Turns out you're a violent, impotent man.

222
00:20:01,200 --> 00:20:02,079
My bad luck.

223
00:20:42,599 --> 00:20:43,519
Am I going crazy?

224
00:21:23,400 --> 00:21:24,160
Triple eights

225
00:21:45,119 --> 00:21:46,200
I'm really losing my mind

226
00:21:46,319 --> 00:21:47,759
How could this be the password?

227
00:22:10,680 --> 00:22:13,200
First day as Zhai Qiuyu's personal doctor

228
00:22:15,640 --> 00:22:17,359
While Zhai Qiuyu was relaxing before the match

229
00:22:17,440 --> 00:22:19,000
His core muscles were too tense

230
00:22:19,200 --> 00:22:21,599
Focus on loosening the quadratus lumborum and gluteus medius

231
00:22:22,160 --> 00:22:23,720
He added an extra half hour today

232
00:22:23,720 --> 00:22:24,319
Strength training

233
00:22:25,039 --> 00:22:26,119
Incredible willpower

234
00:22:48,519 --> 00:22:50,599
Zhai Qiuyu's third day of pre-competition fat control

235
00:22:51,240 --> 00:22:52,839
Weight dropped by 0.5 kg

236
00:22:53,160 --> 00:22:54,799
but muscle condition remained good

237
00:22:55,480 --> 00:22:56,559
During the massage,

238
00:22:56,839 --> 00:22:59,079
he seemed more restless than usual.

239
00:22:59,680 --> 00:23:01,039
He had electrolyte water.

240
00:23:55,400 --> 00:23:57,160
Day after day of scheduled routines,

241
00:23:57,519 --> 00:23:59,519
tireless training intensity,

242
00:23:59,680 --> 00:24:00,680
it seems

243
00:24:00,880 --> 00:24:03,400
there's no more data to record.

244
00:24:12,920 --> 00:24:13,720
Li Youen

245
00:24:15,599 --> 00:24:16,400
Come up

246
00:24:30,599 --> 00:24:31,519
I like him

247
00:24:32,240 --> 00:24:35,079
He's the one who pulled me from darkness into sunlight

248
00:24:52,359 --> 00:24:53,200
Li Youen

249
00:24:53,839 --> 00:24:54,880
Where are you?

250
00:25:08,079 --> 00:25:08,880
Brother

251
00:25:15,480 --> 00:25:18,440
Guess how much I sold today

252
00:25:18,920 --> 00:25:21,279
I bet you sold it all

253
00:25:21,559 --> 00:25:22,359
Clever

254
00:25:23,519 --> 00:25:24,319
Awesome

255
00:25:25,519 --> 00:25:26,400
Let's go home and eat.

256
00:25:26,400 --> 00:25:26,960
Let's go.

257
00:25:59,279 --> 00:25:59,880
I'm eating now.

258
00:26:04,359 --> 00:26:05,039
Brother,

259
00:26:06,160 --> 00:26:07,119
Your cooking

260
00:26:07,759 --> 00:26:08,759
is getting better and better.

261
00:26:09,559 --> 00:26:11,160
These stir-fried meat slices are especially delicious.

262
00:26:14,720 --> 00:26:15,400
Brother,

263
00:26:16,160 --> 00:26:17,279
This fish...

264
00:26:17,359 --> 00:26:18,680
It's not the one that died that day, is it?

265
00:26:21,039 --> 00:26:22,079
No

266
00:26:24,799 --> 00:26:25,359
That's good then

267
00:26:25,759 --> 00:26:26,559
Hurry up and eat

268
00:26:42,759 --> 00:26:43,200
Brother

269
00:26:43,559 --> 00:26:44,319
What's wrong?

270
00:26:44,599 --> 00:26:45,880
I want to sleep with you

271
00:26:57,319 --> 00:26:58,039
What's wrong?

272
00:27:00,000 --> 00:27:00,960
Go to sleep now

273
00:27:14,559 --> 00:27:15,359
Xiaosi

274
00:27:18,359 --> 00:27:19,720
You must be well

275
00:27:39,359 --> 00:27:40,240
Who are you looking for?

276
00:27:45,279 --> 00:27:46,000
It's not him.

277
00:27:47,960 --> 00:27:48,759
It's not.

278
00:28:09,240 --> 00:28:10,559
Can you help me find Li Youen?

279
00:28:10,680 --> 00:28:12,119
Do you think I'm a tracking dog?

280
00:28:12,480 --> 00:28:13,359
Speak of the devil.

281
00:28:13,359 --> 00:28:14,319
I have no other choice.

282
00:28:15,880 --> 00:28:17,359
I just want to talk to him one more time.

283
00:28:18,519 --> 00:28:20,559
But he's vanished into thin air.

284
00:28:21,920 --> 00:28:22,680
Or maybe,

285
00:28:23,640 --> 00:28:25,039
Did he mention to you

286
00:28:25,039 --> 00:28:26,640
any relatives or friends?

287
00:28:37,119 --> 00:28:38,599
The patient who was in this bed before,

288
00:28:38,960 --> 00:28:39,880
the previous one,

289
00:28:40,599 --> 00:28:41,759
was transferred to another hospital, right?

290
00:28:47,359 --> 00:28:48,160
You're saying

291
00:28:48,960 --> 00:28:50,400
where did you hide Li Youen?

292
00:28:50,640 --> 00:28:51,720
I don't know!

293
00:28:51,839 --> 00:28:52,720
I've paid back all the money.

294
00:28:53,200 --> 00:28:54,519
I have no reason to cause him trouble.

295
00:29:02,279 --> 00:29:03,279
It wasn't them either.

296
00:29:04,759 --> 00:29:05,759
Then who could it be?

297
00:29:08,240 --> 00:29:09,319
Where else could he go?

298
00:29:11,640 --> 00:29:12,920
Why isn't this one moving?

299
00:29:13,279 --> 00:29:14,319
Is it dead?

300
00:29:15,359 --> 00:29:16,480
Maybe it's just sleeping.

301
00:29:23,319 --> 00:29:23,960
Brother,

302
00:29:25,519 --> 00:29:26,359
Xiaosi,

303
00:29:27,680 --> 00:29:28,559
Xiaosi,

304
00:29:29,960 --> 00:29:30,640
Xiaosi,

305
00:29:31,160 --> 00:29:32,000
Xiaosi,

306
00:29:32,279 --> 00:29:33,279
Wake up!

307
00:30:16,400 --> 00:30:17,039
Brother

308
00:30:20,960 --> 00:30:21,720
Does it hurt, brother?

309
00:30:26,400 --> 00:30:26,960
Brother

310
00:30:27,880 --> 00:30:28,720
What's wrong?

311
00:30:29,240 --> 00:30:30,160
It was so hard in the city before

312
00:30:30,160 --> 00:30:31,519
but you were never like this

313
00:30:32,160 --> 00:30:33,119
Now, every day

314
00:30:33,799 --> 00:30:34,960
you're so restless

315
00:30:35,279 --> 00:30:36,400
I'm really worried about you

316
00:30:36,400 --> 00:30:36,920
Every day

317
00:30:37,319 --> 00:30:38,160
Every day

318
00:30:39,039 --> 00:30:40,839
It's like your mind is full of things

319
00:30:42,319 --> 00:30:43,119
Brother

320
00:30:44,519 --> 00:30:47,640
Do you want to go back?

321
00:30:56,640 --> 00:30:57,279
Hello?

322
00:30:57,839 --> 00:30:58,640
Teacher Li?

323
00:30:58,920 --> 00:31:00,480
Qiu Yu hit Chen Mo.

324
00:31:00,480 --> 00:31:01,880
He was disqualified by the organizing committee.

325
00:31:01,880 --> 00:31:03,079
Did you see the news?

326
00:31:03,359 --> 00:31:04,839
Zhai Qiuyu was disqualified.

327
00:31:07,319 --> 00:31:08,279
It has nothing to do with me.

328
00:31:10,559 --> 00:31:11,400
Zhai Qiuyu.

329
00:31:13,119 --> 00:31:14,680
You don't want to hear his name.

330
00:31:15,200 --> 00:31:15,839
Brother,

331
00:31:16,160 --> 00:31:17,960
Did you leave the club because of him?

332
00:31:19,000 --> 00:31:20,799
He's that eccentric boss, isn't he?

333
00:31:21,960 --> 00:31:23,920
It was my fault that he got disqualified.

334
00:31:25,559 --> 00:31:26,960
I also bear a lot of responsibility.

335
00:31:26,960 --> 00:31:28,759
You're responsible for him hitting someone.

336
00:31:30,480 --> 00:31:31,279
Xiaosi,

337
00:31:32,880 --> 00:31:33,759
you don't understand.

338
00:31:39,279 --> 00:31:40,839
I'm going inside to rest for a bit.

339
00:31:45,039 --> 00:31:45,720
Brother,

340
00:31:52,599 --> 00:31:54,240
are you here to mock me?

341
00:31:55,119 --> 00:31:56,359
Or do you want to report my current state

342
00:31:56,359 --> 00:31:57,799
to Chen Mo?

343
00:32:22,359 --> 00:32:23,440
I've thought of a way

344
00:32:23,440 --> 00:32:24,720
to stop that girl from being sad.

345
00:32:25,359 --> 00:32:26,240
Which girl?

346
00:32:26,480 --> 00:32:28,440
The one we stole that day when we were drunk.

347
00:32:29,359 --> 00:32:30,720
A way to stop Brother Qiuyu from being sad...

348
00:32:30,720 --> 00:32:31,960
I haven't even found one.

349
00:32:32,839 --> 00:32:34,559
How could I possibly be in the mood for some girl?

350
00:32:34,920 --> 00:32:36,119
He can't get over it.

351
00:32:36,119 --> 00:32:37,440
It's because he feels he wronged Li Youen.

352
00:32:38,079 --> 00:32:39,200
Why are you worrying about him?

353
00:32:41,279 --> 00:32:42,599
Because we're friends.

354
00:32:52,319 --> 00:32:54,000
A friend you think about even in bed

355
00:32:55,880 --> 00:32:57,160
Why are you talking like that?

356
00:33:14,880 --> 00:33:15,960
What is this place?

357
00:33:19,680 --> 00:33:20,880
Are you serious?

358
00:33:21,359 --> 00:33:22,839
You're showing a photo from over twenty years ago

359
00:33:22,839 --> 00:33:23,680
and asking who he is?

360
00:33:23,839 --> 00:33:24,640
Twenty years ago?

361
00:33:24,920 --> 00:33:25,880
How old was he then?

362
00:33:28,000 --> 00:33:29,559
Why would Li Youen be here?

363
00:33:31,240 --> 00:33:31,920
This

364
00:33:35,400 --> 00:33:36,759
This is Youen Ge's hometown.

365
00:33:36,960 --> 00:33:38,119
He said before

366
00:33:38,799 --> 00:33:40,039
that he would definitely return.

367
00:33:42,200 --> 00:33:43,000
Zhai Qiuyu,

368
00:33:43,599 --> 00:33:45,000
why did you ask Li Youen to come back?

369
00:33:45,680 --> 00:33:46,759
To keep bullying him?

370
00:33:48,920 --> 00:33:50,960
He can't just leave like this, in limbo.

371
00:33:52,359 --> 00:33:53,599
Even if we're to cut ties,

372
00:33:55,480 --> 00:33:56,799
you have to explain it to me clearly.

373
00:33:58,799 --> 00:33:59,680
Qiuyu Ge.

374
00:34:07,839 --> 00:34:09,400
You can't just tell everyone everything.

375
00:34:09,679 --> 00:34:11,119
Li Youen wouldn't like that.

376
00:34:11,239 --> 00:34:12,960
We should at least give Brother Qiu Yu a chance.

377
00:34:12,960 --> 00:34:14,079
I took him home that day when I'd had too much to drink.

378
00:34:14,079 --> 00:34:15,400
Isn't that giving him a chance?

379
00:34:15,559 --> 00:34:17,079
But look at what he's done.

380
00:34:17,320 --> 00:34:18,000
I think

381
00:34:18,239 --> 00:34:19,880
he hasn't even figured out if he likes someone or not.

382
00:34:19,880 --> 00:34:21,000
Of course he likes her.

383
00:34:22,079 --> 00:34:22,880
He just

384
00:34:23,280 --> 00:34:24,800
doesn't know how to say he likes her.

385
00:34:24,800 --> 00:34:26,719
But he can curse someone out, one sentence after another.

386
00:34:27,360 --> 00:34:28,599
If you say you like someone, you won't.

387
00:34:30,719 --> 00:34:32,360
Where do you get off being so generous?

388
00:34:33,039 --> 00:34:34,320
Teacher Li's departure this time

389
00:34:34,440 --> 00:34:35,639
Brother Qiu Yu must really regret it.

390
00:34:35,639 --> 00:34:37,119
That's his own doing, though.

391
00:34:37,840 --> 00:34:39,440
And you're feeling wronged for him?

392
00:35:03,880 --> 00:35:05,039
I'm flying to Shenjiang tonight.

393
00:35:05,880 --> 00:35:07,159
To discuss the sculpture exhibition.

394
00:35:14,320 --> 00:35:15,119
Other things,

395
00:35:16,679 --> 00:35:17,800
Let's talk about it when I get back.

396
00:35:32,360 --> 00:35:33,199
What's wrong with you?

397
00:35:33,840 --> 00:35:35,119
How could you do the surgery yourself?

398
00:35:35,719 --> 00:35:36,639
I'm eager to take my vacation.

399
00:35:36,960 --> 00:35:38,039
Take... vacation.

400
00:35:39,960 --> 00:35:41,280
Aren't you suspended for three months?

401
00:35:41,840 --> 00:35:43,800
Perfect. I can take my vacation then.

402
00:35:44,000 --> 00:35:44,639
You

403
00:35:45,360 --> 00:35:47,079
You accepted that pretty quickly.

404
00:35:48,079 --> 00:35:49,679
But you should have at least discussed it with us!

405
00:35:50,000 --> 00:35:51,480
That way, we could have made some news out of it.

406
00:35:52,159 --> 00:35:53,000
I don't have time.

407
00:35:53,360 --> 00:35:54,440
You're suspended.

408
00:35:54,639 --> 00:35:55,800
How can you not have time?

409
00:36:02,199 --> 00:36:04,320
I have something very important to do.
